org.tapchain.realworld

クラス CanvasFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.app.Fragment
      • org.tapchain.realworld.CanvasFragment
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class CanvasFragment
extends android.app.Fragment
    CanvasFragment controls creation of canvas view and canvas model. CanvasFragment is set for retaining instance so that canvas model is not recreated. Created by hiro on 2015/12/26.
